    "",
    "Which testing areas should we focus on for the test suite?",
    "",
    "      1. Unit tests - Unit tests for core logic and utilities ",
    "      2. Integration tests - Integration tests for provider connectivity",
    "      3. E2E tests - End-to-end tests simulating real sessions",
    "      4. Benchmark tests - Benchmark tests for startup and response times",
    "      5. Mutation tests - Mutation tests to validate assertion quality",
    "      6. Type a custom option - Other",
